      "text": "Match the following drugs with the conditions they are used to treat:\n\n \n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\tConditions\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\tDrugs\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t1. Delirium Tremens\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\ta. Naloxone\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t2. Acute Alcoholism\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\tb. Oxazepam\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t3. Smoking Cessation\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\tc. Acamprosate\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t4. Opioid Poisoning\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\td. Varenicline",
